## 2026-04-04 - ExportPanel live preview debounce
- Added 250ms debounced auto-re-export: when `results.length > 0` (preview is showing) and export-affecting settings change (`selected`, `cssSelector`, `selectedSets`, `selectedTypes`, `pathPrefix`, `changesOnly`, `diffPaths`, `connected`), the export automatically re-runs after 250ms idle, keeping the preview in sync without hammering the server on every keystroke/toggle.
- Used "stable callback ref" pattern: `livePreviewFnRef.current = handleExport` on every render so the timer always calls the latest closure; `livePreviewHasResultsRef.current = results.length > 0` avoids putting `results` in deps (which would cause an infinite re-export loop since each export updates `results`).
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/ExportPanel.tsx` ~L811-L826

