## 2026-04-04 - Manual snapshot restore has no concurrency guard
- Added promise-chain mutex (`lockChain` + `withLock`) to `ManualSnapshotStore` serializing all mutating operations: `save()`, `delete()`, and `restore()`. Concurrent `restore()` calls now queue behind each other so journal writes and token-set iteration never interleave.
- Files changed: `packages/server/src/services/manual-snapshot.ts` ~L58-67 (lockChain field + withLock helper), ~L109 (save), ~L164 (delete), ~L253 (restore)
- **Learnings for future iterations:**

